\pard{\pntext\f0 (36)\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlbody\pnf0\pnindent360\pnstart36\pndec{\pntxtb(}{\pntxta)}}
\fi-390\li1110\sl480\slmult1\tx1110\ldblquote Bioheat\rdblquote  shall mean a fuel comprised of biodiesel blended with conventional \par
