\pard\sl480\slmult1 various rooms of a building.\par
\pard\noline\hyphpar0\fi900\li-180\ri-180\sl480\slmult1\qj\cf1\ulnone\'a75. \cf0 Chapter 3 of title 6 of the administrative code of the city of New York is amended by adding a new subchapter 7 to read as follows:\par
\pard\noline\hyphpar0\li-180\ri-180\sl480\slmult1\qc\ul SUBCHAPTER 7\par
Bioheat\par
\pard\fi720\sl480\slmult1\'a76-317\tab\tab Bioheat.\b\par
\b0\'a76-317 Bioheat. a. (1) \cf1 Beginning on January 1, 2009, all heating oil purchased for use in any building owned and operated by the city shall be bioheat containing not less than ten percent biodiesel.  \par
(2) Beginning on January 1, 2011, all heating oil purchased for use in any building owned and operated by the city shall be bioheat containing not less than twenty percent biodiesel.  \par
b. \cf0 Subdivision b of section 6-303 of this chapter shall not apply to this subchapter.\cf1\par
\pard\sl480\slmult1\ulnone\tab\'a76. This local law shall take effect immediately upon its enactment.\par
